          },
          "blocks": {
            "accordion_row_pcXW9Y": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "You've got four main series. What's the actual difference?",
                "content": "",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_7EtcXB": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p><strong>Supreme (The Workhorse):</strong> Your durable, reliable first great knife.</p><p><strong>Retro (The Upgrade):</strong> A big step up. Stays seriously sharp, for longer.</p><p><strong>Mo (The Stunner):</strong> All the sharpness of the Upgrade, in a beautiful Damascus finish.</p><p><strong>LAN (The Pro):</strong> Our absolute best. Elite steel for an edge that just doesn't quit.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_7EtcXB"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_6tQbnh": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Is the wavy 'Damascus' pattern on the Mo and LAN series real?",
                "content": "",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_g7yrea": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Oh, 100%. That’s not a cheap laser-etch you’ll see on knock-offs. </p><p>It’s the real, beautiful result of folding 67+ layers of steel over that high-performance core. It looks incredible, and it even helps food slide right off the blade. This is the real deal.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_g7yrea"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_BCTefQ": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_dash_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "So... can I put my knife in the dishwasher?",
                "content": "",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_4yTDmM": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>That's the one hard \"no.\" A dishwasher's high heat and harsh soap are brutal on a sharp blade and a beautiful handle.</p><p><strong>The simple fix:</strong> Just give it a 10-second hand wash with warm, soapy water right after use. Done.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_4yTDmM"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_wRmVEU": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_dash_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Aren't these just 'Made in China' knives?",
                "content": "",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_HxKVBr": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Yep. They’re made in Yangjiang, the \"Capital of Knives.\"</p><p>Here’s a fun fact: Yangjiang has been mastering this craft for over 1,400 years. That’s centuries before the famous hubs in Germany and Japan even got started.</p><p>So we take world-class steel, send it to the city with the longest history of making world-class blades, and skip the legacy-brand markups. It’s not just a good knife; it's a smart one.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_HxKVBr"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_4Tg8BV": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_dash_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What's the warranty? What if I don't like it?",
                "content": "",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_e7gcyQ": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Easy. If it's not love at first slice, send it back within 30 days for a full refund.</p><p>You're also covered by a lifetime warranty against manufacturing defects. And as a 100% Aussie company, you’re always protected by Australian Consumer Law. We’ve got your back.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
